OOC: This is attack phase 2 if you get this before part one wait it will get 
there I hope.

::Inu-Yasha::
Watches the timer in his optics "Ok My move" Inu activates his cloak and 
flies up extremely high above the registered Air defense sweeps of the 
Alliance base.

::Koj::
Cuts on the projector and enters his Tekno battle mode and gets ready to 
make a running start.

::The Holo Image::
As a medium sized ship looking like its been through hell streams toward the 
defense grid.

::Inu-Yasha::
Inu goes on all com frequencys as he watches the image "This is the White 
Tiger My ship has taken heavy damage I'm not going to make it I'm launching 
5 pods this my crew please help them......." the transmission ends suddenly.

::The Holo Image::
The ship explodes before reaching the Alliance ((estimated)) scan grid.

::Inu-Yasha::
Activates the 5 Stasis pod's transwarp cells each takes off streaming toward 
driffent points around the Alliance base outside there shield area.((Whoever 
goes after each of the pods from the moment you get in range 5ft stop or try 
to open stop if you like.))

::Koj::
Koj gets ready to rush in the second shields. Koj Chants Slowly in his head 
and the bracelet play music for him alittle louder "You can't hero hiding 
underneath your bed."  switchs his jets to silent running.
